-- Solar Trust Venture in U.S. to Seek Listed Company Merger, Manager Reports
-- B y   M i k e   G a v i n
-- 2010-11-17T09:57:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-17/solar-trust-venture-in-u-s-to-seek-listed-company-merger-manager-reports.html
(Corrects headline to show article based on report in
magazine.)  Solar Trust of America LLC, a joint
venture of German companies Solar Millennium AG and Ferrostaal
AG, plans to merge in the medium term with a U.S. listed
company, Manager-Magazin reported, citing people inside the
companies.  Solar Trust, which is planning an approximately 1-gigawatt
solar plant in California, wants to be listed in the U.S. to
help gain funding for projects, the magazine reported. A capital  increase is not planned for the present, it said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mike Gavin at 
 mgavin2@bloomberg.net  